t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\">Features:</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">10 ASSORTED MEASURING TOOLS - Beille measuring tool set comes with 10 assorted cups and spoons for cooking and baking in essential sizes - 1 cup, 1/2 cup, 1/3 cup, 1/4 cup, 1/8 cup, 1tsp, 1/2 tsp, 1 tsp, 1 Tbsp and 1/2 Tbsp; Must-have set of measuring tools for food and meal prep</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">PLANT-BASED MATERIAL - Measuring cups and spoons are made of wheat straw (bioplastic); plant-based material not made from fossil fuels making it more sustainable; Innovative material is a great zero-waste option; Certified BPA free (food-grade safe)</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SOLID AND DURABLE - Beille wheat straw measuring cups mimic traditional plastic measuring tools without harmful byproducts. Cups and spoons are dishwasher safe and are safe for both hot and cold food prep items</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">STACKABLE DESIGN - All spoons and cups fit neatly inside of each other for easy storage and organization when not in use; Handles feature slots and come with a matching keyring for hanging storage if preferred; Stylish beige/cream color will fit your kitchen decor</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-left\"></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<td class=\"attr-right td-list-item\">SPECIFICATIONS - Color: beige/cream/off-white; Material: 60% wheat straw/40” polypropylene; Sizes included: 1 cup, 1/2 cup, 1/3 cup, 1/4 cup, 1/8 cup, 1tsp, 1/2 tsp, 1 tsp, 1 Tbsp and 1/2 Tbsp, Dimensions of stacked set: 6” x 3”</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t</div><!-- /product-specs -->\n\t\t</div>\n\t\t<div class=\"col-md-6\">\n\t\t\t<h1>Beille 10 Piece Kitchen Measuring Cups Spoons Cooking Baking Set Wheat Straw</h1>\n\t\t\t<h2>MSRP <span class=\"msrp-strike\">14.99</span></h2>\n\t\t\t<p>Want to step up your cooking and baking game? Then you need the Beille 10pc Measuring Tools Set made with wheat straw! These measuring cups and spoons are made with an innovative plant-based material called wheat straw that mimics classic measuring tools without the harmful byproducts of traditional plastic.\n\nWheat straw is a bioplastic that is not made from fossil fuels making it more sustainable and a great zero-waste option. It’s certified BPA-free and is food-grade safe so you can count on it for food and meal prep.\n\nThe measuring tools set comes with 10 assorted cups and spoons in essential cooking and baking sizes: 1 cup, 1/2 cup, 1/3 cup, 1/4 cup, 1/8 cup, 1tsp, 1/2 tsp, 1 tsp, 1 Tbsp, and 1/2 Tbsp. All tools included are dishwasher safe and safe for use with both hot and cold food prep ingredients.\n\nWith a conveniently stackable design, these measuring tools all fit neatly inside of each other for easy storage and organization when not in use. The handles come with a slot and matching keyring so you can hang them to store and dry if preferred. They come in a stylish and modern cream/beige color that will fit perfectly with just about any kitchen decor.</p>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"d-flex d-flex-col grid-60 center text-center bg-grey\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-header m-all-1rem all-caps\">Newsletter</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-100\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>SUBSCRIBE for Early Access to Sales</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>Up to 90% Off</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"grid-80 center\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"newsletter-link\" href=\"https://my.ebay.com/ws/eBayISAPI.dll?AcceptSavedSeller&amp;sellerid=dealsonlywebstore\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newsletter-btn all-caps\">Sign Up</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\